column2: SELECT TOP # p.objid, p.ra,p.dec,p.petror9#_r, p.dered_g, p.z, s.zErr, zns.nvote, zns.p_el as elliptical, zns.p_dk as dontknow, zns.p_mg as merger   FROM Galaxy as p    JOIN ZooNoSpec AS zns ON p.objid = zns.objid    JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE p.clean=# and zns.nvote >= # and zns.p_cw > #
